These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, puzzles, hiking, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, software-developer, electrician, journalist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, disco, blues, pop
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
 3. the fan blues is not to the right of the fan disco##8
 4. the fan disco is not to the left of the journalist##8
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an even position##4
 6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the fan blues##1
 7. the writer is the fan r&b##1
 8. the fan blues is not the journalist##6
 9. the fan disco is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the electrician##8
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
12. the fan disco is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the software-developer##2
13. the fan blues and the electrician have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |     3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking | puzzles      | video-games | magic-tricks |
| Job           | electrician | journalist | software-developer      | writer |
| Music-Genre   | blues        | disco            | pop    | r&b |

