.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, coffee, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, funk, trance, blues
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, cricket, snowboarding, handball
 1. the fan trance is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
 2. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 3. the person who's sport is cricket and the fan disco have the same parity positions##9
 4. the fan trance is somewhere to the right of the fan blues##5
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person drinking mirinda##8
 7. the fan blues is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking coffee##2
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the fan funk##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan blues##1
11. the fan disco is not to the left of the person who's sport is handball##8
12. the fan blues is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
13. the fan blues is on the left of the fan trance##1
14. the fan trance is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage      | mirinda | soy-milk   | coffee     | cola     |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | disco   | blues      | trance    |
| Sport         | handball   | cricket | snowboarding | skateboarding |

