.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography, card-games, cooking
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, turkish, argentine
4 different pets are kept: fish, pony, cat, goat
 1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the spanish##8
 2. the turkish is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 3. the turkish is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the turkish is somewhere between the argentine and the owner of the pony##7
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking and the spanish have different parity positions##9
 6. the owner of the cat is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
 8. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 9. the nigerian is on the left of the spanish##1
10. the owner of the fish is between the spanish and the owner of the goat##2
11. the person who's hobby is photography is not the spanish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |    4    |
| Hobby         | cooking | card-games     | magic-tricks  | photography |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | spanish    | turkish | argentine |
| Pet           | cat       | pony | fish     | goat  |

