.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing, skydiving, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, water-polo, handball, skateboarding
 1. the person drinking lemonade and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
 2. the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing have different parity positions##9
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 5. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | milk        | lemonade  | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing  | video-games    | skydiving | filmmaking |
| Sport      | handball | parkour | skateboarding | water-polo    |

