.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-9-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, water, 7up
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, peach, grapes, eggplant
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, train, roller
 1. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
 2. the person eating cranberry and the person drinking soy-milk have different parity positions##9
 3. the person driving the roller is the person drinking water##1
 4. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person driving the ship##8
 5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 6. the person drinking milk and the person eating grapes have different parity positions##9
 7. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
 8. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 9. the person eating cranberry and the person drinking 7up have the same parity positions##9
10. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | water | milk | soy-milk      | 7up        |
| Food        | grapes  | cranberry       | eggplant     | peach  |
| Transport   | roller      | train        | ship | bus |

