4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, snake, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, snowboarding, biathlon
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
 4. the australian is on the right of the russian##1
 5. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 6. the russian is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
 7. the indian and the person who's sport is basketball have different parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
 9. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
10. the russian is not to the right of the australian##8
11. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who's sport is basketball##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |       4       |
| Nationality   | russian | australian    | indian   | thai       |
| Pet           | bird    | snake   | hedgehog | goldfish        |
| Sport         | biathlon  | volleyball | snowboarding     | basketball |

 